talk to Sir Wartoshika about you and me.

79
00:10:52,031 --> 00:10:55,364
Caesar, you are a good man.

80
00:10:56,936 --> 00:11:00,372
<i>But l still don't feel it.</i>

81
00:11:01,407 --> 00:11:04,035
