came to save my life.

86
00:11:18,992 --> 00:11:21,825
<i>Sharon!
Astral! Stay away!</i>

87
00:11:23,196 --> 00:11:25,289
<i>l don't want to believe he's dead.</i>

88
00:11:25,832 --> 00:11:27,823
<i>l'm sorry, Caesar.</i>

89
00:11:30,269 --> 00:11:34,205
